<topic id="managing-datastage-test-data"><title>managing datastage test data</title><body/><topic id="editing-a-datastage-test-case"><title>Editing a DataStage test case</title><body><p>You can edit DataStage test cases either from the Asset browser or directly from within the DataStage designer canvas.</p><p><b>From the asset browser</b></p><ol><li>Open an existing project project.</li><li>Click New asset + &gt; Create DataStage test case.</li></ol><p><b>From the DataStage canvas</b></p><ol><li>Open an existing DataStage flow or create a new flow.</li><li>Click the <b>Test cases</b> icon to open up the Test cases side panel.</li><li>Click <b>New test case +</b></li></ol></body></topic><topic id="learn-more"><title>Learn more</title><body><p><xref format="html" href="learn-more"/></p><ul><li>Authoring test data</li><li>Fabricating test data</li><li>Capturing test data</li></ul></body></topic></topic>